<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thagau Thiengtho khuva nunnem,
 Hung lengin ka hun ngai ui;
 Hun suhalh kitin la mipi chaute,
 Muolliem loin hung kit inla.

[V2]
 Aw, ka hun ngai ui Thagau nunnem,
 Nang loin mipite a gammang ui;
 Puikit inla aw, Zingsawl Aksi Zion,
 Nawpna lampi thiengah.

[V3]
 2. Ngaitie Lalpa Na tatsate.
 Kumsawt hinna lam mang ui;
 Lei belampute hin a pui thei puou,
 Bangti ahi ta dem Lalpa?

[V4]
 3. Thagau Thiengtho, Nang na um chun,
 Khawvel lungkham a nem sek;
 Gitlohna leh buoina gal lien mah leh,
 Na min pakin zaila sangka.

[V5]
 4. Isu nunnem hung tau kitin,
 Lungkham taka Na thawkna;
 Hetsak inla aw Na linglukhuk tawh,
 Na thavaihna mak tak cheng tawh.</lyrics>
<title>Thagau Nunnem!</title>
<hymn_number>104</hymn_number>
<author>Upa Zasiama</author>
</song>